snippet.title: Early gameplay of Trouble Hunter Chronicles
snippet.description:
Just showing some early gameplay of Trouble Hunter Chronicles - the upcoming point and click adventure game!

We don't want to give away much so all you'll see is some parts of town and hear some nice background mucis - we even skip the intro to avoid spoilers!

Check out the game and wishlist it: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1355360/Trouble_Hunter_Chronicles_The_Stolen_Creed/
